hh3cMulticastSnoop.name: hh3cMulticastSnoop

revisions.description: The initial version of this MIB file.

hh3cMulticastSnoop.contactinfo: Platform Team Hangzhou H3C Tech. Co., Ltd. Hai-Dian District Beijing P.R. China http://www.h3c.com Zip:100085

hh3cMcsGlobalConfigTable.name: hh3cMcsGlobalConfigTable
hh3cMcsGlobalConfigTable.description: Table containing information about the global configuration of IGMP/MLD snooping.

hh3cMcsGlobalConfigEntry.name: hh3cMcsGlobalConfigEntry
hh3cMcsGlobalConfigEntry.description: Entry containing information about the global configuration of IGMP/MLD snooping.

hh3cMcsGlbSnoopingType.name: hh3cMcsGlbSnoopingType
hh3cMcsGlbSnoopingType.description: Type of the global configuration. IPv4 means IGMP snooping configuration, and IPv6 means MLD snooping configuration.

hh3cMcsGlbRowStatus.name: hh3cMcsGlbRowStatus
hh3cMcsGlbRowStatus.description: The activation of a row enables IGMP/MLD snooping globally. The destruction of a row disables IGMP/MLD snooping globally.

hh3cMcsGlbEntryLimit.name: hh3cMcsGlbEntryLimit
hh3cMcsGlbEntryLimit.description: Global maximum number of IGMP/MLD snooping forwarding entries.

hh3cMcsGlbHostAgingTime.name: hh3cMcsGlbHostAgingTime
hh3cMcsGlbHostAgingTime.description: Global aging time of the multicast group on ports.

hh3cMcsGlbRouterAgingTime.name: hh3cMcsGlbRouterAgingTime
hh3cMcsGlbRouterAgingTime.description: Global aging time of router ports.

hh3cMcsGlbDropUnknownEnabled.name: hh3cMcsGlbDropUnknownEnabled
hh3cMcsGlbDropUnknownEnabled.description: Whether the feature of dropping unknown packets is enabled globally.

hh3cMcsVirtualUnitConfigTable.name: hh3cMcsVirtualUnitConfigTable
hh3cMcsVirtualUnitConfigTable.description: Table containing configuration information about the specified VLAN or VSI.

hh3cMcsVirtualUnitConfigEntry.name: hh3cMcsVirtualUnitConfigEntry
hh3cMcsVirtualUnitConfigEntry.description: Entry containing information of the specified VLAN or VSI.

hh3cMcsVUID.name: hh3cMcsVUID
hh3cMcsVUID.description: VLAN ID or VSI Index. Its value ranges from 1 to 4094 when type is VLAN, and from 0 to 0xFFFFFFFE when type is VSI

hh3cMcsVUSnoopingType.name: hh3cMcsVUSnoopingType
hh3cMcsVUSnoopingType.description: Type of the configuration. IPv4 means IGMP snooping configuration, and IPv6 means MLD snooping configuration.

hh3cMcsVURowStatus.name: hh3cMcsVURowStatus
hh3cMcsVURowStatus.description: The activation of a row enables IGMP/MLD snooping in the VLAN or VSI. The destruction of a row disables IGMP/MLD snooping in the VLAN or VSI.

hh3cMcsVUHostAgingTime.name: hh3cMcsVUHostAgingTime
hh3cMcsVUHostAgingTime.description: Aging time of the multicast group on ports in the VLAN or VSI. A value of zero indicates that it is not configured in the VLAN or VSI.

hh3cMcsVUMaxResponseTime.name: hh3cMcsVUMaxResponseTime
hh3cMcsVUMaxResponseTime.description: Maximum query response time in the VLAN or VSI. A value of zero indicates that it is not configured in the VLAN or VSI.

hh3cMcsVURouterAgingTime.name: hh3cMcsVURouterAgingTime
hh3cMcsVURouterAgingTime.description: Aging time of the router port in the VLAN or VSI. A value of zero indicates that it is not configured in the VLAN or VSI.

hh3cMcsVULastMemQryInterval.name: hh3cMcsVULastMemQryInterval
hh3cMcsVULastMemQryInterval.description: Last member query interval in the VLAN or VSI. A value of zero indicates that it is not configured in the VLAN or VSI.

hh3cMcsVUDropUnknownEnabled.name: hh3cMcsVUDropUnknownEnabled
hh3cMcsVUDropUnknownEnabled.description: Whether the feature of dropping unknown packets is enabled in the VLAN or VSI.

hh3cMcsVUPimSnoopingEnabled.name: hh3cMcsVUPimSnoopingEnabled
hh3cMcsVUPimSnoopingEnabled.description: Whether PIM snooping is enabled in the VLAN or VSI.

hh3cMcsVUVersion.name: hh3cMcsVUVersion
hh3cMcsVUVersion.description: Version of IGMP/MLD snooping that is running on the VLAN. Value 2 represents IGMPv2 snooping and MLDv1 snooping, and value 3 represents IGMPv3 snooping and MLDv2 snooping.

hh3cMcsVUQuerierEnabled.name: hh3cMcsVUQuerierEnabled
hh3cMcsVUQuerierEnabled.description: Whether the querier feature is enabled in the VLAN or VSI.

hh3cMcsVUGeneQuerierSourceAddress.name: hh3cMcsVUGeneQuerierSourceAddress
hh3cMcsVUGeneQuerierSourceAddress.description: Source IP address of IGMP or MLD general query packets. Its value is 255.255.255.255 or FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF when not configured.

hh3cMcsVUSpecQuerierSourceAddress.name: hh3cMcsVUSpecQuerierSourceAddress
hh3cMcsVUSpecQuerierSourceAddress.description: Source IP address of IGMP or MLD group-specific query packets. Its value is 255.255.255.255 or FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF when not configured.

hh3cMcsVULeaveSourceAddress.name: hh3cMcsVULeaveSourceAddress
hh3cMcsVULeaveSourceAddress.description: Source IP address of IGMP or MLD leave packets. Its value is 255.255.255.255 or FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF when not configured.

hh3cMcsVUReportSourceAddress.name: hh3cMcsVUReportSourceAddress
hh3cMcsVUReportSourceAddress.description: Source IP address of IGMP or MLD report packets. Its value is 255.255.255.255 or FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF when not configured.

hh3cMcsL2EntryTable.name: hh3cMcsL2EntryTable
hh3cMcsL2EntryTable.description: Table containing a list of Layer 2 multicast group entries.

hh3cMcsL2EntryEntry.name: hh3cMcsL2EntryEntry
hh3cMcsL2EntryEntry.description: Entry of l2-multicast group, which is created for each group learned or configured in the VLAN or VSI.

hh3cMcsL2EntryVUID.name: hh3cMcsL2EntryVUID
hh3cMcsL2EntryVUID.description: VLAN ID or VSI Index. Its value ranges from 1 to 4094 when type is VLAN, and from 0 to 0xFFFFFFFE when type is VSI.

hh3cMcsL2EntryGroupAddress.name: hh3cMcsL2EntryGroupAddress
hh3cMcsL2EntryGroupAddress.description: IP address of the multicast group which the port joined.

hh3cMcsL2EntrySourceAddress.name: hh3cMcsL2EntrySourceAddress
hh3cMcsL2EntrySourceAddress.description: IP address of the unicast source which the port joined.

hh3cMcsL2EntryIfIndex.name: hh3cMcsL2EntryIfIndex
hh3cMcsL2EntryIfIndex.description: IfIndex value of the port that joined the Layer 2 IP multicast group entry.

hh3cMcsL2EntryPortAttribute.name: hh3cMcsL2EntryPortAttribute
hh3cMcsL2EntryPortAttribute.description: Attribute of the port. 'd' means learned from IGMP/MLD packets, 's' means configured statically, 'p' means learned from PIM snooping, 'k' means obtained from the kernel, 'r' means learned from (*, *) entries, 'w' means learned from (*, G) entries.

hh3cMcsPacketStatisticsTable.name: hh3cMcsPacketStatisticsTable
hh3cMcsPacketStatisticsTable.description: Table containing the IGMP/MLD packets statistics.

hh3cMcsPacketStatisticsEntry.name: hh3cMcsPacketStatisticsEntry
hh3cMcsPacketStatisticsEntry.description: Entry containing the statistic information of IGMP/MLD packets that have been transmitted and received in the device.

hh3cMcsStatisticsSnoopingType.name: hh3cMcsStatisticsSnoopingType
hh3cMcsStatisticsSnoopingType.description: Type of the snooping, IPv4 means the statistics for IGMP snooping, and IPv6 means the statistics for MLD snooping.

hh3cMcsRxGeneryQueryNum.name: hh3cMcsRxGeneryQueryNum
hh3cMcsRxGeneryQueryNum.description: Statistics of IGMP or MLD general query packets received on the device.

hh3cMcsRxV2SpecificQueryNum.name: hh3cMcsRxV2SpecificQueryNum
hh3cMcsRxV2SpecificQueryNum.description: Statistics of IGMPv2 or MLDv1 group-specific query packets received on the device.

hh3cMcsRxV3SpecificQueryNum.name: hh3cMcsRxV3SpecificQueryNum
hh3cMcsRxV3SpecificQueryNum.description: The statistics of IGMPv3 or MLDv2 group-specific query packets received on the device.

hh3cMcsRxV3SpecificSGQueryNum.name: hh3cMcsRxV3SpecificSGQueryNum
hh3cMcsRxV3SpecificSGQueryNum.description: Statistics of IGMPv3 or MLDv2 group-and-source-specific query packets received on the device.

hh3cMcsRxV1ReportNum.name: hh3cMcsRxV1ReportNum
hh3cMcsRxV1ReportNum.description: Statistics of IGMPv1 report packets received on the device.

hh3cMcsRxV2ReportNum.name: hh3cMcsRxV2ReportNum
hh3cMcsRxV2ReportNum.description: Statistics of IGMPv2 or MLDv1 report packets received on the device.

hh3cMcsRxV3ReportNum.name: hh3cMcsRxV3ReportNum
hh3cMcsRxV3ReportNum.description: Statistics of IGMPv3 or MLDv2 report packets received on the device.

hh3cMcsRxV3ErrCorReportNum.name: hh3cMcsRxV3ErrCorReportNum
hh3cMcsRxV3ErrCorReportNum.description: Statistics of IGMPv3 or MLDv2 report packets with correct and incorrect records received on the device.

hh3cMcsRxLeaveNum.name: hh3cMcsRxLeaveNum
hh3cMcsRxLeaveNum.description: Statistics of leave packets received on the device.

hh3cMcsRxPimHelloNum.name: hh3cMcsRxPimHelloNum
hh3cMcsRxPimHelloNum.description: Statistics of PIM hello packets received on the device.

hh3cMcsRxErrorPacketNum.name: hh3cMcsRxErrorPacketNum
hh3cMcsRxErrorPacketNum.description: Statistics of error IGMP/MLD packets received on the device.

hh3cMcsTxV2SpecificQueryNum.name: hh3cMcsTxV2SpecificQueryNum
hh3cMcsTxV2SpecificQueryNum.description: Statistics of IGMPv2 or MLDv1 group-specific query packets sent from the device.

hh3cMcsTxV3SpecificQueryNum.name: hh3cMcsTxV3SpecificQueryNum
hh3cMcsTxV3SpecificQueryNum.description: Statistics of IGMPv3 or MLDv2 group-specific query packets sent from the device.

hh3cMcsTxV3SpecificSGQueryNum.name: hh3cMcsTxV3SpecificSGQueryNum
hh3cMcsTxV3SpecificSGQueryNum.description: Statistics of IGMPv3 or MLDv2 group-and-source-specific query packets sent from the device.

hh3cMcsPortJoinGroupConfigTable.name: hh3cMcsPortJoinGroupConfigTable
hh3cMcsPortJoinGroupConfigTable.description: Table for configuring a port as a simulated member host for a multicast group.

hh3cMcsPortJoinGroupConfigEntry.name: hh3cMcsPortJoinGroupConfigEntry
hh3cMcsPortJoinGroupConfigEntry.description: Entry for configuring a port as a simulated member host for a multicast group.

hh3cMcsPortJoinGroupIfIndex.name: hh3cMcsPortJoinGroupIfIndex
hh3cMcsPortJoinGroupIfIndex.description: Port for which this entry contains information.

hh3cMcsPortJoinGroupSnoopingType.name: hh3cMcsPortJoinGroupSnoopingType
hh3cMcsPortJoinGroupSnoopingType.description: Type of the configuration. IPv4 means IGMP snooping configuration, and IPv6 means MLD snooping configuration.

hh3cMcsPortJoinGroupVlanID.name: hh3cMcsPortJoinGroupVlanID
hh3cMcsPortJoinGroupVlanID.description: Index uniquely identifying the specified VLAN in which a host on a port joined the multicast group.

hh3cMcsPortJoinGroupGroupAddress.name: hh3cMcsPortJoinGroupGroupAddress
hh3cMcsPortJoinGroupGroupAddress.description: IP address of the group to which the host belongs.

hh3cMcsPortJoinGroupSourceAddress.name: hh3cMcsPortJoinGroupSourceAddress
hh3cMcsPortJoinGroupSourceAddress.description: IP address of the source. A value of zero indicates that the multicast packets of this group can come from any sources.

hh3cMcsPortJoinGroupStatus.name: hh3cMcsPortJoinGroupStatus
hh3cMcsPortJoinGroupStatus.description: This object is responsible for managing rows, which supports 'active', 'createAndGo' and 'destroy'.

hh3cMcsPortStaticGroupConfigTable.name: hh3cMcsPortStaticGroupConfigTable
hh3cMcsPortStaticGroupConfigTable.description: Table for configuring static group membership entries on a port.

hh3cMcsPortStaticGroupConfigEntry.name: hh3cMcsPortStaticGroupConfigEntry
hh3cMcsPortStaticGroupConfigEntry.description: Entry for configuring static group membership entries on a port.

hh3cMcsPortStaticGroupIfIndex.name: hh3cMcsPortStaticGroupIfIndex
hh3cMcsPortStaticGroupIfIndex.description: Port for which this entry contains information.

hh3cMcsPortStaticGroupSnoopingType.name: hh3cMcsPortStaticGroupSnoopingType
hh3cMcsPortStaticGroupSnoopingType.description: Type of the configuration. IPv4 means IGMP snooping configuration, and IPv6 means MLD snooping configuration.

hh3cMcsPortStaticGroupVlanID.name: hh3cMcsPortStaticGroupVlanID
hh3cMcsPortStaticGroupVlanID.description: Index uniquely identifying the specified VLAN in which a port statically joined the multicast group.

hh3cMcsPortStaticGroupGroupAddress.name: hh3cMcsPortStaticGroupGroupAddress
hh3cMcsPortStaticGroupGroupAddress.description: IP address of the multicast group.

hh3cMcsPortStaticGroupSourceAddress.name: hh3cMcsPortStaticGroupSourceAddress
hh3cMcsPortStaticGroupSourceAddress.description: IP address of the source. A value of zero indicates that the multicast packets of this group can come from any sources.

hh3cMcsPortStaticGroupStatus.name: hh3cMcsPortStaticGroupStatus
hh3cMcsPortStaticGroupStatus.description: This object is responsible for managing the creation and deletion of rows, which supports 'active', 'createAndGo' and 'destroy'.

hh3cMcsRouterPortConfigTable.name: hh3cMcsRouterPortConfigTable
hh3cMcsRouterPortConfigTable.description: Table for configuring a port as a static router port.

hh3cMcsRouterPortConfigEntry.name: hh3cMcsRouterPortConfigEntry
hh3cMcsRouterPortConfigEntry.description: Entry for configuring a port as a static router port.

hh3cMcsRouterPortConfigIfIndex.name: hh3cMcsRouterPortConfigIfIndex
hh3cMcsRouterPortConfigIfIndex.description: Port for which this entry contains information.

hh3cMcsRouterPortConfigSnoopingType.name: hh3cMcsRouterPortConfigSnoopingType
hh3cMcsRouterPortConfigSnoopingType.description: Type of the configuration. IPv4 means IGMP snooping configuration, and IPv6 means MLD snooping configuration.

hh3cMcsRouterPortConfigVlanID.name: hh3cMcsRouterPortConfigVlanID
hh3cMcsRouterPortConfigVlanID.description: Index uniquely identifying the specified VLAN in which a port act as a static router port.

hh3cMcsRouterPortConfigRowStatus.name: hh3cMcsRouterPortConfigRowStatus
hh3cMcsRouterPortConfigRowStatus.description: This object is a conceptual row entry that allows to add or delete entries to or from the hh3cMcsRouterPortConfigTable. When an entry is created in this table 'createAndGo' method is used and the value of this object is set to 'active'. Deactivation of an 'active' entry is not allowed. When an entry is deleted in this table 'destroy' method is used.

hh3cMcsPortConfigTable.name: hh3cMcsPortConfigTable
hh3cMcsPortConfigTable.description: Table for configuring the fast leave status, group limit number, group policy parameter and overflow replace status on a port in the specified VLAN.

hh3cMcsPortConfigEntry.name: hh3cMcsPortConfigEntry
hh3cMcsPortConfigEntry.description: Entry containing information about the fast leave status, group limit number, group policy parameter and overflow replace status of a port in the specified VLAN.

hh3cMcsPortConfigIfIndex.name: hh3cMcsPortConfigIfIndex
hh3cMcsPortConfigIfIndex.description: Port for which this entry contains information.

hh3cMcsPortConfigSnoopingType.name: hh3cMcsPortConfigSnoopingType
hh3cMcsPortConfigSnoopingType.description: Type of the configuration. IPv4 means IGMP snooping configuration, and IPv6 means MLD snooping configuration.

hh3cMcsPortConfigGroupLimitNumber.name: hh3cMcsPortConfigGroupLimitNumber
hh3cMcsPortConfigGroupLimitNumber.description: Group limit number of the port.

hh3cMcsPortConfigFastLeaveStatus.name: hh3cMcsPortConfigFastLeaveStatus
hh3cMcsPortConfigFastLeaveStatus.description: Fast leave status of the port.

hh3cMcsPortConfigGroupPolicyParameter.name: hh3cMcsPortConfigGroupPolicyParameter
hh3cMcsPortConfigGroupPolicyParameter.description: ACL number which is used as the group policy parameter of the port.

hh3cMcsPortConfigOverflowReplace.name: hh3cMcsPortConfigOverflowReplace
hh3cMcsPortConfigOverflowReplace.description: This object is related to the object hh3cMcsPortConfigGroupLimitNumber. If the current group number is less than the value of hh3cMcsPortConfigGroupLimitNumber, any new group is permitted. If the current group number equals to the value of hh3cMcsPortConfigGroupLimitNumber and the value of this object is enabled, the group with the minimum multicast address will be replaced by the new group. If the current group number equals to the value of hh3cMcsPortConfigGroupLimitNumber and the value of this object is disabled, none of new group will be permitted.

hh3cMcsPortConfigRowStatus.name: hh3cMcsPortConfigRowStatus
hh3cMcsPortConfigRowStatus.description: The object is responsible for managing the creation and deletion of rows, which supports 'active', 'createAndGo' and 'destroy'.
